### Get Item by ID
GET http://localhost:8000/api/items/1

### Create New Item
POST http://localhost:8000/api/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sample Product",
  "description": "A sample product for testing",
  "quantity": 50,
  "price": 29.99,
  "category": "Electronics"
}

### Get Top Items by Category
GET http://localhost:8000/api/items/category/Electronics/top

### Create Temporary Block
POST http://localhost:8000/api/items/block/temporary
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "itemId": 1,
  "quantity": 5
}

### Convert to Permanent Block
POST http://localhost:8000/api/items/block/permanent
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "blockId": 1
}

### Clean Expired Blocks
POST http://localhost:8000/api/items/cleanup/expired-blocks